{"tid":1968563,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(有片) 尼日利亞國會議長 傳召「中國」領事, 投訴「中國」歧視尼日利亞人","createTime":"2020-04-11T18:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T10:44:11.000Z","uid":134071,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ba7a0e4c2f6726bfe87e42f6260e3b7fa900179e","tid":1968563,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:12:24.000Z","msg":"尼日利亞人在廣州遭隔離 大使奪人爆衝突 (有片)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.soundofhope.org/post/365608?lang=b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.soundofhope.org%2Fpost%2F365608%3Flang%3Db5&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=68469797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.soundofhope.org/post/365608?lang=b5</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>而家, 尼日利亞國會議長Oloye Akin Alabi傳召「中國」領事，投訴國民响中國不人道歧視，要求星期二交代。(亦係有片)</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/akinalabi/status/1248690552486400001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fakinalabi%2Fstatus%2F1248690552486400001&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=eb6a7ed1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fakinalabi%2Fstatus%2F1248690552486400001&h=b648e8d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/akinalabi/status/1248690552486400001</a>"},{"pid":"632392dbfb0b1fb9968c92f596857867a60c25c5","tid":1968563,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:13:14.000Z","msg":"Oloye Akin Alabi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n補充內容<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/goodbyehkhellouk/photos/a.155136541681491/791178234743982/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgoodbyehkhellouk%2Fphotos%2Fa.155136541681491%2F791178234743982%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=c505c79e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/goodbyehkhellouk/photos/a.155136541681491/791178234743982/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\nGoodbye HK, Hello UK<br />\n2 小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n尼日尼亞國會議長傳召中國領事，投訴國民响中國不人道歧視，要求星期二交代。<br />\n<br />\n仲拍埋成個對話內容放上網，點估得到「亞非拉」好朋友反而係最激嗰個？<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;As a government, we will not allow Chinese or other nationals to be maltreated just as we will not allow Nigerians to be maltreated in other countries.&quot;<br />\n（作為政府，我地唔會虐待中國或者其他國家嘅人，同樣我地唔想見到自己嘅國民比其他國家虐待。）<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;It appears that is what happened in this case; you cannot use one brush to smear the whole wall. Whatever the reason, it cannot be used and taken out on the entire community in China.&rdquo;<br />\n（跟據呢件事黎睇，你地總唔能夠用一把尺度晒所有人㗎。無論如何，呢個概念亦唔應該响中國社會出現囉。）"},{"pid":"a168763a66129248c229c4c44252a2fc39cc9cb3","tid":1968563,"uid":19126,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:17:13.000Z","msg":"直接立即屌佢老母啦，唔洗俾時間佢交代架喇，因間話果啲人係收美國佬錢扮黑人抹黑中共架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae621dff509ee0e43d8f90bf45adb2a6a0a8744","tid":1968563,"uid":276989,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />習近平親自指揮既外宣輸到仆街"},{"pid":"9bc245284833c48651cd8a967402cc1a3e9fda1b","tid":1968563,"uid":25603,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:32:52.000Z","msg":"各位一定要CLS！<br />\nC: Comment<br />\nL: Like<br />\nS: Share"},{"pid":"f12c5b43b6b074d93b45441ab57e6b83013e94da","tid":1968563,"uid":56819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:36:52.000Z","msg":"狗咬主人?"},{"pid":"38740cdbef935cf2e4d445e40bec656b8b8a58bd","tid":1968563,"uid":66202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:38:32.000Z","msg":"可能過多幾日就會話尼日利亞係病毒源頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":